title: Liverpool star Danny Ings reunited with stunning Australian model girlfriend Georgia Gibbs after she returns from trip
text:
INGS ARE GOOD Liverpool star Danny Ings reunited with stunning Australian model girlfriend Georgia Gibbs after she returns from trip 
Injured striker's spirits lifted after his partner returns from Indonesia trip BY GARY STONEHOUSE Click to share on Facebook (Opens in new window) Comments LIVERPOOL star Danny Ings received an extra boost in his rehabilitation from injury after he was reunited with his striking girlfriend Georgia Gibbs. 
The forward is out for the rest of the season following knee surgery but looked to be in high spirits following the return of his partner from Indonesian. Instagram @ingstagram10 4 
And he could not wait to share the reunion with is fans, posting a selfie with Gibbs on his Instagram account. 
Keep up-to-date with all the latest transfer news and gossip ahead of the January window with SunSport’s daily LIVE blog. 
The glamorous blonde, who shot to fame on Australia’s Next Top Model, had also previously posted ‘you make my heart sing’ alongside a montage of the pair together. related articles HOU DARES WINS Aston Villa set to land Conor Hourihane with Barnsley ace determined to sign for Steve Bruce again LUK WHO'S STAYING Everton strike ace Romelu Lukaku plays down talk of a January move back to former club Chelsea Transfers live All the latest breaking news and gossip from the January transfer window Title winner set to leave Striker Leonardo Ulloa wants a move away from champions Leicester with four clubs keen 
He also missed the majority of last season with a similar injury. 
Liverpool fans will have to wait until the next campaign to see him back on the pitch, but team-mate Joe Gomez believes he will be back better than ever. 
Gomez, who was also out for most of the 2015/16 season, said recently: “It wasn’t easy for me hearing about Ingsy’s injury because he’s someone I am close to. Manchester Evening News Ings is out for the rest of the season Instagram @ingstagram10
